(210, 1, '2015-03-25 08:50:09', '2015-03-25 08:50:09', 'Critical Mission Computing has been designing, developing and re-engineering successful software applications since its inception in 1999. Our motto is to consistently exceed your expectations as our valued client. We strive to help your business progress and prosper through support for constant growth. \r\n\r\nWe have designed several bespoke software systems to make business function in a simpler, faster and efficient manner. Market research, time management, cost effectiveness and efficiency are the key components of our solutions. \r\n\r\nWe offer targeted solutions because our team members have varied interests in different fields which helps us collectively to offer you the best overall solutions to your requirements. \r\n\r\nWe also have options to help you improve one or more aspects of your organisation. The accuracy of our programs encourages more hits and concept clarity ensures retaining client interest in the site to give your business maximum opportunity. \r\n \r\nWe understand the value of your success because it ensures the ongoing journey of Critical Mission Computing. ', 'Who We Are', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-25 08:50:09', '2015-03-25 08:50:09', '', 15, 'http://dothejob.in/cop-cms/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
