(359, 1, '2015-03-31 07:22:36', '2015-03-31 07:22:36', '<strong>Industry:</strong> Recruitment Consultant\r\n<strong>Overview</strong>\r\nKings Recruitment Consultant is a leading No. 1 Supplier of Print &amp; Facilities, providing Temporary, Permanent and Contract personnel to support all Business Support areas. They are specializing in Digital Document Management, from Origination and Design through to Printing, Output to CD, Binding and Finishing.\r\n<strong>Services Offered</strong>\r\nCritical Mission Computing offered Application Development, Quality Assurance and Technical Support services.\r\n<strong>Challenges</strong>\r\nConvert 14 years old VB desktop application into a web application\r\nManage Huge database of clients and candidates\r\nParity Calculations\r\nCoordinate, change, recalculate the Financial Calender for the change of each financial year\r\nFull management of the Transfer utility\r\nWindows Server to Linux Based Server Platform Migration.\r\n<strong>Solutions</strong>\r\nConvert Desktop (VB) application in Web Application using Cake PHP.\r\nMigrate huge database into new system with new directory structure\r\nFile Formation\r\nManage Directories Structure\r\nDevelopment Environment\r\nPHP Version 5.4, Cakephp Version 2.4.6, Mysql Version 5.5, PhpDocx , PhpExcel\r\n<strong>Extensions Utilized</strong>\r\n1. Libreoffice\r\n2. poppler-utils\r\n3. ZIP support\r\n4. XSL support\r\n5. DOM support\r\n6. SimpleXML support\r\n7. Tidy support\r\n8. Server centos\r\nTeam Size: 6+\r\n<strong>Engagement Overview:</strong>\r\nThe Managing Director of Kings gave an understanding of running functionalities of the VB (Desktop Application) system and architecture in Feb 2014.\r\nFirst step was to set up the development environment for the application. Initial set of tasks for the developers was to review running VB application, which gave the opportunity to developers to understand the concept of the requirement.\r\nThe next set of tasks involved implementing complete application in CakePHP with Mysql database.\r\nThe QA team was assigned the responsibility to develop the test plan, and test data for several important functionalities for the coming releases. They were also made responsible for testing the functionalities.\r\nThe project was divided into various milestones to meet delivery time frame throughout the project.\r\nA complete new Replenishment module was developed by the team from Feb 2014 to July 2014.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Kings Recruitment Consultant', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kings-recruitment-consultant', '', '', '2015-04-24 08:50:07', '2015-04-24 08:50:07', '', 0, 'http://dothejob.in/cop-cms/?post_type=our-solution&#038;p=359', 1, 'our-solution', '', 0),
