(361, 1, '2015-03-31 07:30:38', '2015-03-31 07:30:38', 'Holistic healing denotes continuous growth of body, mind and soul. It is an undeniable fact that the cycle of one’s life has been interspersed with imminent contradictions of ups and downs, good and bad, pros and cons, positives and negatives, happiness and grief, success and failure – which brings about ‘change’, which is also inevitable. When faced with change or difficulties in our life which we find too painful to accept, we tend to hold these unresolved thoughts, emotions, memories or actions in our aura which creates blockages. Such blockages in our energy fields or aura lead to suffering, depression or disease.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAn Energy Healer is a facilitator who assists in identifying these blockages and releasing them, with an aim to ensure balanced growth. This enables healing at all levels&amp;#45;&amp;#45;physical, mental, emotional and spiritual. Energy healing is thus a holistic approach which spurs the return journey to health. The resultant changes can be profound and noticeable to everybody or they can be subtle and only felt by the person herself/himself.', 'Holistic Healings', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'holistic-healings', '', '', '2015-04-24 13:44:12', '2015-04-24 13:44:12', '', 0, 'http://dothejob.in/cop-cms/?post_type=our-solution&#038;p=361', 3, 'our-solution', '', 0),
(362, 1, '2015-03-31 07:31:56', '2015-03-31 07:31:56', '3T (Triumph  Through Training) which is a  dynamic Training &amp; Development company founded and managed by highly qualified core group of  professionals and experts, having vast experience and exposure. 3T act as catalyst for continuous learning, personal and professional growth and for increasing overall effectiveness.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n3T have been providing training programs to Corporates (Indian and Multinationals), Educational Institutions (Universities, Colleges, Schools), Government Institutions, NGO’s, and Professionals (CA, CS, Doctors, Engineers). They have focused on improving the performance of companies by improving their teams’ performance across industries. Their clients range from India’s premier UV and Farm equipment company, Cement manufacturers, IT companies, FMCG product manufacturers, Hotels and Hospitals, Telecommunications equipment and service providers, Insurance company, Wind Energy company, Global Infrastructure engineering, Procurement and Construction Companies (EPC), Real Estate, Jewellery manufacturer and exporters, Media, to Logistics and Warehousing leaders in North India.', 'Trainings For All', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trainings-for-all', '', '', '2015-04-24 09:06:06', '2015-04-24 09:06:06', '', 0, 'http://dothejob.in/cop-cms/?post_type=our-solution&#038;p=362', 2, 'our-solution', '', 0),
